i", "b": "oil", "w": 1}, {"a": "trading", "b": "wti", "w": 1}, {"a": "oilandgas", "b": "trading", "w": 1}, {"a": "gasoline", "b": "usa", "w": 1}, {"a": "oilgas", "b": "oilprice", "w": 1}, {"a": "iran", "b": "iranwar", "w": 1}, {"a": "energy", "b": "oilgas", "w": 1}]}, "top_tweets": [{"id": "2074378107952275677", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074378107952275677", "text": "Iran is making another push to direct all Hormuz traffic to its shipping lanes, away from the Omani side. It has fired to several vessels this morning. \n\nPart of its plan seems, too, allowing multiple Japanese ships to cross: yesterday 6 Japanese oil tankers crossed, and 2 more are crossing today.", "time": "06:20", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 73179, "likes": 303, "replies": 22, "retweets": 66, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 34, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2074390086721102078", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2074390086721102078", "text": "Global commodities CTA positioning.\n\nDefinitely seeing highly overcrowded spaces right now. The trade is just begging for a clean reversal catalyst to wake up the tape.\n\n#oott #gold #copper https://t.co/7ugbWweFd2", "time": "07:08", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 22825, "likes": 150, "replies": 7, "retweets": 21, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 63, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2074409552401908128", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074409552401908128", "text": "COLUMN: China giveth and China taketh away.\n\nOil won't rise to $100 a barrel again this year or drop to $50 in 2027 if China keeps behaving as the rational energy trader we’ve seen in recent months.\n\n@Opinion https://t.co/ozzdurgvNY", "time": "08:25", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 63301, "likes": 368, "replies": 27, "retweets": 72, "quotes": 12, "bookmarks": 82, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["China demand", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2074435628209725713", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2074435628209725713", "text": "Saudi-Flagged Crude Oil Tanker Damaged Near Strait of Hormuz After Separate LNG Tanker Collision. #OOTT", "time": "10:09", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 26825, "likes": 146, "replies": 13, "retweets": 30, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 13, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2074493461194055719", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074493461194055719", "text": "US SPR sales so far were around 96 million barrels, total sales volumes is 132.5 million barrels, so another 36.5 million barrels will be released over the coming weeks #oott", "time": "13:59", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 19018, "likes": 74, "replies": 3, "retweets": 15, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2074515813131006026", "url": "https://x.com/antonisbabo/status/2074515813131006026", "text": "#oott outfit of the ton ㅋㅋ https://t.co/9Kl4nQVPL1", "time": "15:28", "author": "antonisbabo", "author_name": "바보", "followers": 39618, "views": 52118, "likes": 1804, "replies": 0, "retweets": 611, "quotes": 162, "bookmarks": 198, "labels": {"relevant": false, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": []}}, {"id": "2074516511612449069", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074516511612449069", "text": "Iran has attacked at least two (and probably tree) oil/LNG tankers in the last 24 hours in the Strait of Hormuz. If history serves of any guide, the US is likely to retaliate soon against Tehran. All SoH traffic has gone, again, dark, with vessels switching off their AIS.", "time": "15:30", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 130868, "likes": 533, "replies": 38, "retweets": 97, "quotes": 7, "bookmarks": 40, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2074518601978011883", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074518601978011883", "text": "Israel's energy minister touts oil pipeline to bypass Hormuz #oott https://t.co/o4slG6GhHe", "time": "15:39", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 28057, "likes": 7, "replies": 1, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2074540282373177736", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074540282373177736", "text": "While Iran attacked today at least 3 oil and LNG tankers in the Strait of Hormuz, it was rather busy loading its own tankers at Kharg Island. Activity in the major Iranian oil terminal has picked up significantly from previous weeks. 📷 @CopernicusEU Sentinel-2 🛰️ https://t.co/UVMaAPli48", "time": "17:05", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 37802, "likes": 232, "replies": 20, "retweets": 57, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 22, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2074555475165626561", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074555475165626561", "text": "US SPR crude inventories in million barrels - orange line is EIA's projection #oott https://t.co/xnfnasVjkm", "time": "18:05", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 9212, "likes": 47, "replies": 12, "retweets": 8, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 5, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2074569858428059904", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074569858428059904", "text": "BREAKING: US revokes the sanctions waiver on Iran’s oil and petrochemical sales after Tehran attacked several tankers earlier today in the Strait of Hormuz https://t.co/fhJKO8lJD8", "time": "19:02", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 192324, "likes": 646, "replies": 46, "retweets": 233, "quotes": 24, "bookmarks": 82, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2074593946706035132", "url": "https://x.com/BroadStreetOil/status/2074593946706035132", "text": "#API\n\nCrude: -.399\nCush: -.069\nDist: -1.801\nGas: -2.929\n\n #OOTT", "time": "20:38", "author": "BroadStreetOil", "author_name": "RD", "followers": 459, "views": 35681, "likes": 11, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories", "Refining/products"]}}, {"id": "2074594405118345303", "url": "https://x.com/JuliOnTwtr/status/2074594405118345303", "text": "API inventory moves 07/07/26\n\nCrude -399,000 (est. -1.5 million)\nGasoline -2.929 million \nDistillates  -1.801 million \nCushing  -69,000\n\nSPR (actual) -6.2 million \n\n#oott #crudeoil #api #gasoline", "time": "20:40", "author": "JuliOnTwtr", "author_name": "Julianne Geiger", "followers": 8674, "views": 44676, "likes": 281, "replies": 21, "retweets": 54, "quotes": 16, "bookmarks": 16, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bulli